== About
I am a final year Ph.D. student at IIT Hyderabad, advised by [https://www.iith.ac.in/~vineethnb/ Prof. Vineeth N Balasubramanian]. My research focuses on trustworthy machine learning and on multimodality, with recent work on enhancing visual reasoning in Multimodal Language Models.
You can find my CV [srinivas_cv_latest2026.pdf here].

== Research Interests
- Visual reasoning in Multimodal LLMs (spatial reasoning, grounding, RLVR/RL post-training)
- Human-in-the-loop / preference-aware learning (algorithmic recourse)
- Robustness, interpretability, and reliability of ML systems

